<% brand_name = @brand_membership.brand.name -%>
Welcome to Larp Library!
========================

<%
paragraph_text = <<-EOF.strip
Larp Library is a site for larp authors to publish their work under free-to-use
licenses.
EOF

paragraph_text << if @inviting_user
  "  #{@inviting_user.name} has invited you to join #{brand_name} on Larp Library."
else
  "  You've been invited to join #{brand_name} on Larp Library."
end
-%><%= paragraph_text %>

This membership allows you to:

* Publish larps as <%= brand_name %>
* Edit existing <%= brand_name %> larps
<% if @brand_membership.admin? -%>
* Add and remove members from #{brand_name}
* Edit the public description and branding for #{brand_name}
<% end -%>

To accept this invitation, go to: <%= absolute_url("/brands/#{@brand_membership.brand.to_param}/invitations/#{@brand_membership.to_param}") %>

If you don't want to join <%= @brand_membership.brand.name %>, please just ignore this email (and possibly let <%= @inviting_user.name %> know).
